        "TextSection": {
            "TextSectionType": "Definition",
            "Contents": "Bloom syndrome is a rare disorder associated with pre- and postnatal growth deficiency a telangiectatic erythematous rash of the face and other sun-exposed areas insulin resistance and predisposition to early onset and recurrent cancer of multiple organ systems."
        },
